detail.msg: Value error, Image content must be a URL (starting with 'https') or base64 encoded image (starting with 'data:image/<format>;base64,<image-base64>'). Received: data:application/pdf;base64,JVBERi0xLjcKJeLjz9MKNz...5kc3RyZWFtCmVuZG9iagpzdGFydHhyZWYKNTg1MTkKJSVFT0YK

messages.content:
<instructions>
Analyze the provided PDF document and answer the given question.
Provide a clear and concise answer based on the content found in the PDF.
Include relevant quotes to support the answer.
</instructions>

Input will be provided in the user message using a JSON following the schema:
```json
{
  "$defs": {
    "PDF": {
      "properties": {
        "content_type": {
          "description": "The content type of the file",
          "examples": [
            "image/png",
            "image/jpeg",
            "audio/wav",
            "application/pdf"
          ],
          "type": "string"
        },
        "data": {
          "description": "The base64 encoded data of the file",
          "type": "string"
        },
        "url": {
          "description": "The URL of the image",
          "type": "string"
        }
      },
      "type": "object"
    },
    "File": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "number": {
          "type": "integer",
          "description": "The index of the file message"
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "properties": {
    "pdf": {
      "$ref": "#/$defs/PDF",
      "description": "The PDF document to analyze"
    },
    "question": {
      "description": "The question to answer about the PDF content",
      "type": "string"
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "pdf",
    "question"
  ],
  "type": "object"
}
```

Return a single JSON object enforcing the following schema:
```json
{
  "properties": {
    "answer": {
      "description": "The answer to the question based on the PDF content",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "quotes": {
      "description": "Relevant quotes from the PDF that support the answer",
      "items": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "type": "array"
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "answer",
    "quotes"
  ],
  "type": "object"
}
```
